content: Research Note (Study ACU-445): Participant RK-29 (DOB 08/12/1991) completed vestibular rehabilitation at Bothell Balance Center under Dr. Mira Patel's supervision. Treatment included weekly sessions using computerized dynamic posturography from 04/2023-06/2023. Concurrent insurance claims show coordination between Policy #GKRS-229 coverage and supplemental PT benefits under Group Plan NW-882.
